and the Soul-guarding Bead.)

24
00:02:14,079 --> 00:02:16,120
(So she must have been taken)

25
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:18,279
(to the Altar of Souls.)

26
00:02:30,839 --> 00:02:32,639
Tan Er!

27
00:02:42,839 --> 00:02:43,919
(This is a serious matter.)

28
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,960
(I can't let them get involved in this.)

29
00:02:47,199 --> 00:02:48,240
What's wrong?

30
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:51,760
It's nothing.

31
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:52,999
It's only a minor headache.

32
00:02:53,919 --> 00:02:55,800
