36
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:05,880
Eighth Brother.

37
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,760
Do not keep secrets from me again.

38
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,240
Do you know

39
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,559
a place known as

40
00:03:31,999 --> 00:03:32,919
