41
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:35,040
I heard it was forbidden ground.

42
00:03:35,279 --> 00:03:36,600
But I've never been there before.

43
00:03:36,999 --> 00:03:37,919
I have no idea

44
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:39,279
whether it existed or not.

45
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:40,639
Not only does it exist,

46
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,560
its entrance...

47
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,079
is right inside Her Majesty's bedroom.

48
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:48,440
Why would Her Majesty summon
Second Princess to the Altar of Souls?

49
00:03:49,639 --> 00:03:51,319
When I was in the palace for the prayer ritual,

50
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:54,000
I stumbled upon that place.

51
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:57,039
There is a strange bead at the altar.

52
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,440
That bead

53
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,680
is closely related to Tan Er.

54
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:02,599
I think Her Majesty

55
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,960
wants to use this bead and Second Princess

56
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,199
to increase her might.

57
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,680
