62
00:04:17,919 --> 00:04:18,639
Back then,

63
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:19,879
Her Majesty

64
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:21,639
tried to alienate Second Princess and me.

65
00:04:22,319 --> 00:04:23,560
