this matter from different perspectives.

80
00:04:51,039 --> 00:04:52,159
Is it my fault?

81
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:53,720
Or should Her Majesty take the blame?

82
00:04:53,759 --> 00:04:54,479
Eighth Brother!

83
00:04:54,479 --> 00:04:55,919
From what I remember,

84
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,879
status and power

85
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,440
would never make you submit.

86
00:05:18,199 --> 00:05:20,079
(The Soul-guarding Bead is really here.)

87
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:22,639
(So in this parallel universe,)

88
00:05:22,639 --> 00:05:24,479
(the Soul-guarding Bead belongs
to the Qu family too.)

89
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:27,240
(Is she the host in this world?)

90
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:28,159
(Does it mean)

91
00:05:28,159 --> 00:05:30,359
(Cheng Cheng and I can return
to our world with the bead?)

92
00:05:35,359 --> 00:05:37,000
(Did the Soul-guarding Bead backfire on her)

93
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,159
(while harnessing its power?)

94
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,079
(But Xiao Zhen)

95
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:40,440
(brought me here)

96
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:42,039
(and forced me to admit)

97
00:05:42,039 --> 00:05:43,599
(my relation with the Soul-guarding Bead.)

98
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:45,960
(Is he going to use me as a tribute)

99
00:05:46,039 --> 00:05:47,599
(as Qu Jiang Lin did?)

100
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:49,759
(But I don't have the Soul-parting Xiao.)

101
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,000
Seems like

102
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:54,199
Your Highness remembers what bead this is.

103
