119
00:07:40,359 --> 00:07:42,199
Don't you know the risks?

120
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,440
You know the secrets.

121
00:07:43,479 --> 00:07:44,639
I do.

122
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,039
But I also know

123
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,520
whatever you plan to do

124
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,479
will only push Her Majesty and me

125
00:07:49,479 --> 00:07:51,120
into deeper darkness!

126
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,400
But sadly,

127
00:07:53,599 --> 00:07:55,479
Her Majesty is already deep in the darkness.

128
00:07:56,520 --> 00:07:57,320
Now,

129
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:59,359
let's see if you can save her.

130
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:25,279
The rumor about Her Majesty building a dungeon

131
00:08:25,479 --> 00:08:27,560
