139
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,080
Xiao Zhen lied.

140
00:09:27,159 --> 00:09:28,359
He wants to use Tan Er

141
00:09:28,359 --> 00:09:29,479
to reawaken Her Majesty

142
00:09:29,479 --> 00:09:30,599
with the power of the Soul-guarding Bead!

143
00:09:31,359 --> 00:09:32,640
But if he fails,

144
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:33,880
Tan Er and Her Majesty

145
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:35,000
