148
00:09:42,359 --> 00:09:43,120
Tan Er!

149
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:46,760
Cheng Cheng!

150
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:49,959
Tan Er.

151
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:51,599
Mo Lian Cheng.

152
