166
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,599
I'll warn you again.

167
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,279
Underestimating the bead will bring

168
00:10:15,279 --> 00:10:16,279
catastrophic consequences.

169
00:10:16,599 --> 00:10:18,039
Both Her Majesty and Tan Er

170
00:10:18,039 --> 00:10:19,399
will in grave danger!

171
00:10:19,719 --> 00:10:20,959
Barely no one in the palace

172
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:23,240
