206
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:41,560
Your Majesty.

207
00:13:42,959 --> 00:13:44,440
This is all my fault.

208
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,000
Watch out!

209
00:14:20,599 --> 00:14:23,080
Cheng Cheng. Wake up!

210
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:29,120
Cheng Cheng.

211
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,039
Your Majesty.

212
00:14:35,479 --> 00:14:38,039
(The mark from the backfire is gone.)

213
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,120
Wake up.

214
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:49,760
Cheng Cheng.

215
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:52,800
If anything happens to him,

216
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,200
I will make you pay dearly.

217
00:14:57,959 --> 00:14:59,080
Your Highness!

218
00:14:59,719 --> 00:15:00,839
Lian Cheng!

219
00:15:05,640 --> 00:15:07,120
You broke into the forbidden ground.

220
00:15:07,359 --> 00:15:08,719
But you tried to protect Her Majesty.

221
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,359
Take her and leave.

222
00:15:10,479 --> 00:15:11,640
When Her Majesty is awake,

223
00:15:11,839 --> 00:15:13,519
I'll explain everything to her.

224
00:15:40,044 --> 00:15:45,932
♪A haggard look is left, why do you
remain aloof and indifferent♪

225
00:15:47,422 --> 00:15:52,844
♪Did loving me become too burdensome♪

226
00:15:53,954 --> 00:16:00,738
♪The sky turns Grey as it is about to rain,
covering inevitable pain♪

227
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:02,640
(A day of marriage,)

228
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:04,800
(comes from centuries of fate.)

229
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:06,599
(Our destiny of three lifetimes)

230
00:16:07,399 --> 00:16:08,919
(is like a surreal dream.)

231
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:15,800
(We meet at the wall in three lifetimes,
the blossoms were falling like rain.)

232
00:16:16,359 --> 00:16:20,800
(Our consummations in three different lifetimes
all ended on a canopy bed we shared.)

233
00:16:22,919 --> 00:16:26,440
(The cycle of a nightmare brings about
a lifeless yearning.)

234
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:30,239
(Without sorrow from our parting,)

235
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:33,279
(we will lose faith in our love.)

236
00:16:33,279 --> 00:16:37,352
♪A dream is the one-time, uninhibited indulgence♪

237
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:45,080
(I'm waking from the dream.)

238
00:16:46,399 --> 00:16:49,919
(But I missed the chance to bid her farewell.)

239
00:17:07,999 --> 00:17:14,079
♪Falling into a black hole of stubbornness,
forcefully making up far-fetched lies♪

240
00:17:15,167 --> 00:17:20,927
♪Even though there are
too many sarcastic moves♪

241
00:17:21,375 --> 00:17:28,799
♪Going from lovers to strangers
makes me confused♪

242
00:17:29,183 --> 00:17:35,327
♪A dream is the one-time, uninhibited indulgence♪

243
00:17:35,583 --> 00:17:38,975
♪Do you understand my confusion at all♪

244
00:17:39,231 --> 00:17:42,623
♪All because of your silence♪

245
00:17:42,879 --> 00:17:46,086
♪Why can't you see it?♪

246
00:17:46,086 --> 00:17:49,663
♪Give me a warm embrace♪

247
00:17:50,184 --> 00:17:53,320
♪Do you understand my heartache at all♪

248
00:17:53,320 --> 00:17:54,320
(Cheng Cheng!)

249
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:57,328
♪All because of your recklessly squander♪

250
00:17:57,600 --> 00:17:58,720
(Cheng Cheng.)

251
00:17:58,992 --> 00:18:03,984
♪I'm starting to not understand
whether there is love♪

252
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:07,639
(Cheng Cheng.)

253
00:18:07,824 --> 00:18:13,008
♪I'm beginning to feel pain for knowing love♪

254
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:17,879
Cheng Cheng?

255
00:18:35,919 --> 00:18:37,360
It's been three days.

256
00:18:38,720 --> 00:18:40,480
Why are you still in a coma?

257
00:18:42,639 --> 00:18:44,360
As long as you can wake up,

258
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:47,680
I can serve you tea and give you
a massage every day.

259
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,639
I'll do whatever

260
00:18:51,759 --> 00:18:53,080
you tell me to do.

261
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:07,080
I'll hold you to it.

262
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:12,800
Cheng Cheng, you're awake.

263
00:19:13,879 --> 00:19:15,680
Do you have to wait for me

264
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,159
to make such promises to wake up?

265
00:19:17,560 --> 00:19:19,680
(Having memories from three lifetimes)

266
00:19:19,919 --> 00:19:21,879
(is such a bizarre sensation.)

267
00:19:22,039 --> 00:19:23,600
(The person in front of me)

268
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:25,720
(still looks the same,)

269
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:28,759
(but she has a much more important
place in my heart now.)

270
00:19:28,759 --> 00:19:30,320
Well?

271
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:33,320
Does the wound still hurt?

272
00:19:34,159 --> 00:19:35,919
(Maybe I should withhold from telling her)

273
00:19:35,919 --> 00:19:37,840
(I've regained my memories.)

274
00:19:39,119 --> 00:19:40,279
My wound...

275
00:19:42,039 --> 00:19:43,519
Don't you remember?

276
00:19:46,999 --> 00:19:48,960
Is this another amnesia?

277
00:19:53,639 --> 00:19:54,960
I only remember

278
00:19:55,279 --> 00:19:56,440
that at some point

